2.0.2 - August 23, 2025
=======================

This library is becoming a copylib! The master branch will no longer have
releases. This 2.0.2 release might well be the last.

* Bugs fixed:
  - #24 High score name reverts to the user's real name (Michael Catanzaro)
  - #27 Circular ref between Context and Context.category_request (Michael
    Catanzaro)

2.0.1 - March 10, 2025
